{"text_id":164525,"tokens":["The"," notion"," that"," repetition"," alone"," can"," lead"," to"," improvement"," is"," a"," common"," myth","."," While"," it","'","s"," true"," that"," repetition"," can"," reinforce"," patterns"," and"," habits",","," it","'","s"," not"," necessarily"," the"," case"," that"," those"," patterns"," and"," habits"," are"," optimal"," or"," desirable","."," In"," the"," context"," of"," shooting"," a"," basketball",","," missing"," ","1","0","0","0"," times"," in"," a"," row"," can"," actually"," be"," detrimental"," to"," developing"," good"," shooting"," form",".","\n\n","When"," you"," repeat"," a"," behavior"," or"," action"," numerous"," times",","," your"," body"," begins"," to"," adapt"," and"," learn"," to"," perform"," that"," action"," more"," efficiently","."," However",","," if"," that"," action"," is"," flawed"," or"," inefficient",","," your"," body"," will"," simply"," become"," more"," efficient"," at"," performing"," it"," poorly","."," This"," is"," where"," the"," concept"," of"," '","bad"," muscle"," memory","'"," comes"," in",".","\n\n","Bad"," muscle"," memory"," refers"," to"," the"," idea"," that"," your"," body"," has"," learned"," to"," perform"," a"," movement"," or"," action"," in"," a"," way"," that"," is"," sub","optimal"," or"," incorrect","."," In"," the"," case"," of"," shooting"," a"," basketball",","," if"," you","'","re"," consistently"," shooting"," with"," poor"," form",","," your"," body"," will"," adapt"," to"," that"," form"," and"," make"," it"," easier"," to"," repeat"," those"," poor"," shooting"," motions","."," This"," can"," make"," it"," more"," difficult"," to"," correct"," your"," form"," in"," the"," future",","," as"," your"," body"," has"," learned"," to"," rely"," on"," those"," inefficient"," patterns",".","\n\n","Furthermore",","," research"," has"," shown"," that"," the"," human"," brain"," is"," wired"," to"," repeat"," patterns"," and"," habits",","," even"," if"," they","'","re"," not"," optimal","."," This"," is"," known"," as"," the"," '","re","petition"," effect","',"," where"," our"," brains"," tend"," to"," default"," to"," familiar"," patterns"," and"," habits",","," even"," if"," they","'","re"," not"," the"," most"," effective","."," This"," means"," that"," if"," you","'","re"," consistently"," shooting"," with"," poor"," form",","," your"," brain"," will"," continue"," to"," rely"," on"," those"," patterns",","," making"," it"," more"," difficult"," to"," change"," them",".","\n\n","So",","," to"," answer"," your"," question",","," simply"," shooting"," a"," basketball"," ","1","0","0","0"," times"," in"," a"," row"," without"," proper"," form"," or"," technique"," will"," not"," necessarily"," lead"," to"," improvement","."," In"," fact",","," it"," may"," even"," hinder"," progress"," by"," reinforcing"," bad"," muscle"," memory"," and"," poor"," shooting"," form","."," The"," key"," to"," improvement"," lies"," in"," deliberate"," practice",","," where"," you"," focus"," on"," proper"," technique",","," form",","," and"," execution",","," and"," receive"," feedback"," and"," guidance"," from"," coaches"," or"," trainers","."," Repetition"," can"," be"," a"," valuable"," tool",","," but"," it"," must"," be"," combined"," with"," proper"," instruction"," and"," a"," focus"," on"," deliberate"," practice"," in"," order"," to"," see"," meaningful"," improvement","."],"sub_source":"reddit","model":"llama3-70b","label":1}